msgid ""
"Odoo centralizes every part of your operation. From organizing events and "
"syncing with sponsors and partners to managing event materials with "
"inventory and scheduling staff, Odoo empowers sports event professionals "
"with fully integrated tools."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 協助你集中管理賽事營運的各個環節。由籌辦活動、聯絡贊助商及合作夥伴協調，"
"以至利用庫存功能管理活動用品、編排人手等，Odoo 都為統籌體育賽事的專業人員，提"
