#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <em>Website</em> app to promote sponsors with their logos, "
"descriptions, and (if relevant) booth details so attendees know where to "
"find them."
msgstr ""
"使用網站應用程式，宣傳你的贊助商，包括他們的公司標誌、描述，以及展位詳情（若"
"相關），以便參加者知道可在哪裏找到他們。<em></em>"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>Project app</strong></font> "
"to organize the event by creating tasks, assigning assignees, setting "
"deadlines, and tracking progress."
msgstr ""
"運用<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>專案管理應用程式</strong></font>舉"
"辦各項活動，包括建立不同任務、分配負責人、設定截止期限，以及追蹤工作進度。"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the Barcode app to scan tickets and give participants their race bibs or "
"event packs easily."
msgstr "使用條碼應用程式掃瞄門票，輕鬆為參賽者發放號碼布或選手包。"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the auto-plan feature to assign staff based on their availability and "
"expertise."
msgstr "使用自動規劃功能，根據員工的空閒時間及專業技能，分配他們至適當的崗位。"

